➜学影视剧用手刀，一个下去却把熟睡的人打醒了？是手法不对吗？
http://www.sohu.com/a/416396164_624188	11126
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200904/86ec5d5c3d4b4f90b9a64b377ac07f1f.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不知道大家还记不记得</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">前不久的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一条沙雕新闻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200904/e39ff3aa226c461f96651c116d584bdd.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">看完这新闻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>朕惊了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一是没想到会有人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如此<strong>艺高人胆大</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在这么紧张刺激的时刻</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">实操武侠片里的剧情</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">二是没想到电视剧里</p>            <div class="lookall-box">
<div class="lookall-shadow"></div>
<section class="lookall">
<a href="javascript:;" class="show-all" id="showMore">
<em>展开全文</em>
</a>
</section>
</div>
<div class="hidden-content control-hide">
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>100%晕人的手刀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">实操起来居然</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>这！么！弱！！</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200904/3d2fedf2294042698949b8fd474466bf.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200904/1a4d4200f12340daba89b93c596f1805.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那么究竟是手法不对</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>还是手刀本来就很弱呢？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200904/f68ccde240dd49419f90ff1621d4525d.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在影视剧里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">手刀是种<strong>比麻醉药还强的存在</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">▼</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">麻醉药不仅需要<strong>等发挥药效的时间</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">醒来之后还可能附赠一些<strong>别的问题</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而手刀就不同了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一刀下去<strong>立马晕</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">晕了起来屁事没有</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200904/7769ce7f9d974c87a4aacf4fa56bee5b.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">电视剧里手刀这样的晕法</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在现实生活有个对应的名词叫</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>晕厥</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而日常生活中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">能让人晕厥主要原因就是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>脑供血不足</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200904/8119ccf168704ea4a1b02de5b26451cf.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>如何让脑供血不足呢？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">理论上来说非常简单</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就是<strong>中断一下血往大脑的运输</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">实操起来就更简单了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也就是打打<strong>动脉</strong>啥的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让血液流动进程被打断一下就好了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200904/11f5f56ec2974ba4938c62d122cba1c7.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">其实理由也很简单</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这是他</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">——<strong>压根就没打对地方</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">虽说面对<strong>巨人</strong>的时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">削得一手好后颈肉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是保证你<strong>活下去的最大资本</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">面对<strong>小猫咪</strong>的时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">捏得一手好后颈肉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是保证你<strong>不被揍的最强技能</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200904/f1a65ea5eb1241f88f8c50d6c5a02533.gif" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但可惜的是</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“被掐住命运的后颈”这个说法</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在人类身上并不适用</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">因为把握我们命运的是——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>侧</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>颈</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那些一看就<strong>很致命的动脉</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以及<strong>密密麻麻的神经</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>全都分布在侧颈</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200904/e66c658d3e20412ebc52223bcff6bce8.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">后颈主要是<strong>肉多厚实</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">帮你好好地连着脑袋</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">包着颈椎骨</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">以防你们笑一笑就把头笑掉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以如果想单纯通过</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">手刀击打后颈导致人晕倒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200904/85a60bfb50ff4074ab44735339895ad5.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟想通过打后颈能打晕人</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就得打裂后颈包着的<strong>颈椎骨</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">让里面的<strong>中枢神经</strong>受损</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">从而影响到<strong>脑子</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可你自己捏捏看</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">后颈肉是不是脖子那儿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>最肥厚</strong>的一块地方</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200904/98545075ca654b1eb4aea25568415c1c.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">电视剧虽说扯吧</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">但一般用手刀打晕别人的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">都是<strong>练家子</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">要么有内功要么有蛮力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而平时连个<strong>引体向上都做不到</strong>的你们</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">还想徒手打这里震碎骨头</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>真的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>别想了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200904/e7423d2be4bd432cb838d6c4534959f9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就算你平时训练有素</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">手劲儿还挺大</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可每个人的<strong>耐受程度</strong>又不同</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这就导致你完全无法判断</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>究竟使出什么样的力道</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>才能让一个人只是暂时晕倒</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>而不是让永远都醒不来？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200904/4a9d9f9ea6ae4ea9a32586db7977d676.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">假如你真的成功了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">通过打裂骨头让人晕倒了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那么恭喜你</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200904/7c007d201ed14c7f9f50b2ca2b86b915.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这种骨裂导致的晕倒</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">不会像电视剧里面一样</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">醒来之后啥事都没有</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">轻则脑出血、脑挫伤</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">重则高位截瘫</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">或者直接醒不过来凉了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200904/f59104b838ea4b39966f96e5bc5c8846.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200904/d5ea2f6adfbd435db9f1f9c5d698677f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">既然后颈打人这么危险</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">难度系数还很高</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>那么往侧颈打行吗？</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200904/bf6e703b802c405d8d427c39ec317332.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">通过侧颈导致晕厥的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有个专业的说法</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">叫<strong>颈动脉窦性晕厥</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这个颈动脉窦就在</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">颈部右上方、颌骨下方的位置</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而它</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">可以说是人体的<strong>“死穴”</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200904/3024849d927c42a98aeada2881042104.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">感受到压力一瞬间</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">颈动脉窦</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就会通过神经告诉大脑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“脑铁，我最近压力好大”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">大脑一听</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那是该给大家都降降压了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">于是同步反馈给<strong>心脏</strong>和<strong>血管</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200904/81c6406119c747fca31153d39e7944d0.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这样一操作</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">心率降低</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">血管舒张</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">血压也就降低了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>有效避免了过高的血压</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>对人体造成伤害</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200904/9409908efcbd437aa89d2bbf7cf74b80.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">它感受到的不是轻微的压力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而是一个突如其来的<strong>强力手刀</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那么——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200904/a20b77706b224bc09523082e4b5835ae.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而如果你面对的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是一个<strong>颈动脉窦非常敏感的</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>颈动脉窦综合征</strong>的患者</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那更简单了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你都不用使劲</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就拿按摩的那种力度</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">给他来个<strong>5</strong>秒钟</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200904/6b79bd53a105452197ff7d8c62a88550.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">甚至</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你都不用动手</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>一件比较紧的高领毛衣</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">或者<strong>突然的一次转头</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">他们都有晕的可能</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200904/47ce45fe83d94038b4762ca0d1d3c7a1.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果你只是感觉呼吸困难</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没有晕的迹象</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那么不要激动不要慌张</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">低下头好好看看——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>是不是衣服穿反了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p5.itc.cn/images01/20200904/2bcd1585040845cc9eed3c10d0d4f62f.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">侧颈这块儿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是真的挺危险</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200904/ff5b03de873b462f92fe70381a97b350.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">有对象的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>种草莓</strong>的时候</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">选址就需要谨慎考虑了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没对象的倒是不用担心</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">反正你自个儿<strong>嘬不到脖子</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200904/b59acd307636485d8a2daadb8c216164.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">侧颈这块</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">在进化过程中</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">既没有骨骼保护</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">又埋了一堆致命的动脉神经</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以在我们的潜意识里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是很排斥别人碰自己脖子的</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200904/0ba6fb0ba4154b99940aeca1d48e7b8e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">如果有人能亲你脖子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">甚至往那里嘬上一口</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">证明你们的关系是真的很<strong>铁</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p6.itc.cn/images01/20200904/6a604ad6d6a84eb295faebda06af8dc2.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而这是关系亲密象征外</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">也是人类<strong>占有欲</strong>的表现</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">把草莓种脸上会被女票暴揍</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">种其他地方别人又可能看不到</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只有脖子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">而且是正面能瞧见的那块</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">是个最佳的地址选择</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">一口下去完美表示</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">“这人，我的”</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p8.itc.cn/images01/20200904/40c0ef8c06ec404b8910125d2a7afa96.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">只是这一口</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>不止人是你的了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>人命也是你的了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">毕竟侧颈那块儿本来就只是个皮包肉</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">没啥防御力</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">你这么用力一嘬</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>血块儿</strong>就被你嘬出来了</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200904/e22e17be48134331b26085a43a9cf0ca.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">这嘬出来的血块儿</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">会顺着血管往上跑</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">问题是血管越往上越细</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那这不就得<strong>堵了</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">血管一堵</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">血液循环系统<strong>整个瘫痪</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">那迎接你的只有——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p3.itc.cn/images01/20200904/3ee38899425942a883f21e889d76a9a9.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">所以……</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">种草莓</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就请好好地种在花盆里</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">嘬脖子</p>
<p class="ql-align-center">就请好好地去——</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>嘬</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>鸭</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><strong>脖</strong></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p0.itc.cn/images01/20200904/975d9edf20094e52a8415eb6cde7af9e.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p4.itc.cn/images01/20200904/61e4e0ead2d9480080d795874609be04.jpeg" max-width="600" /></p>
<p class="ql-align-center">本文系【朕说】原创内容</p>
